h<a href="https://twitter.com/jburnmurdoch/status/1750849189834022932">的摘要</a>。</p><p>在我们被带走之前，让我们牢记这是在余地中发生的：几代人之间仍然可以找到政治倾向的大部分差异，而不是在它们之间。<a href="https://twitter.com/jburnmurdoch/status/1750849207567593523">例如</a>，仍然是，英国的年轻男子在移民方面可能比老年人更加自由，只是在过去的几年中，他们没有变得更加自由，而年轻女性则拥有： </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F0ddfa658-e7ec-4930-83a6-bfa71f525cbb_1298x794.png" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F0ddfa658-e7ec-4930-83a6-bfa71f525cbb_1298x794.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F0ddfa658-e7ec-4930-83a6-bfa71f525cbb_1298x794.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F0ddfa658-e7ec-4930-83a6-bfa71f525cbb_1298x794.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F0ddfa658-e7ec-4930-83a6-bfa71f525cbb_1298x794.png 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F0ddfa658-e7ec-4930-83a6-bfa71f525cbb_1298x794.png" width="1298" height="794" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/0ddfa658-e7ec-4930-83a6-bfa71f525cbb_1298x794.png&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark