brary.wiley.com/doi/abs/10.1111/j.1468-0335.2009.00803.x">工人阶级和/或黑人</a>- 旨在代表他们的政党的群体。特朗普<em>仅通过将非法移民视为要解决的问题就</em>可以赢得选民。</p><p>简而言之，特朗普的反对者对他的戏剧感到如此着迷，以至于他们关注了他的政策。他的选民不这么认为。 </p><p class="button-wrapper" data-attrs="{&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.ian-leslie.com/p/five-myths-about-trump?utm_source=substack&utm_medium=email&utm_content=share&action=share&quot;,&quot;text&quot;:&quot;Share&quot;,&quot;action&quot;:null,&quot;class&quot;:null}" data-component-name="ButtonCreateButton"> <a class="button primary" href="https://www.ian-leslie.com/p/five-myths-about-trump?utm_source=substack&utm_medium=email&utm_content=share&action=share"><span>分享</span></a></p><p><a href="https://www.ian-leslie.com/p/five-myths-about-trump">阅读更多</a></p>; 
